high_descs: Go to the right and stand in front of the round table.
Pick the mug up from under the coffee maker.
Go around the table and to the right to face the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and close the door and then open the door and take the mug out.
Go right and then turn to the right to face the coffee maker on the table.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under a coffee maker on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the table, near the apple.
Pick up the coffee cup from the coffee machine.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the coffee cup into the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the table, near the apple.
Put the coffee cup in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled coffee cup into the coffee machine.

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the door
Pick up a mug from the coffee maker
Move to the fridge to the left of you
Chill the mug in the fridge for a moment
Move to the table to the right of you
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee maker on the table.
